T1  - Illiquidity and stock returns: cross-section and time-series effects
AU  - Amihud, Yakov
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 5
IS  - 1
SP  - 31
EP  - 56
PY  - 2002
DA  - 2002/01/01/
SN  - 1386-4181
